<div class="audio-section">
  <div class="audio-section-title">The Building</div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">Welcome to Oyparaploo</div><div class="track-desc">An introduction to the practice and its eighteen grounds.</div></div><div class="track-dur">4:32</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">The Lobby</div><div class="track-desc">Eclipse Prayer Shadow Impossible Mirror. Four stages of seeing.</div></div><div class="track-dur">6:15</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">The Grounds</div><div class="track-desc">Why grounds, not rooms. Why entrances, not pages.</div></div><div class="track-dur">3:48</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">The Tagline</div><div class="track-desc">For the love of The English. The facade and the trap door.</div></div><div class="track-dur">5:22</div></div>
</div>

<div class="audio-section">
  <div class="audio-section-title">The Writing</div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">Wonderful Garbage</div><div class="track-desc">The founding text. Why transformation of discarded material is a position.</div></div><div class="track-dur">7:10</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">The Three-Layer System</div><div class="track-desc">Lovely Quietness, verification, Master revision. No shortcuts.</div></div><div class="track-dur">8:45</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">Pressure Ghosts</div><div class="track-desc">What remains after the doomed have been forgotten.</div></div><div class="track-dur">6:30</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">The Receiver Turn</div><div class="track-desc">The shift from testimony to invitation.</div></div><div class="track-dur">5:55</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">Finding the Spine</div><div class="track-desc">What the piece actually says, underneath what you thought it said.</div></div><div class="track-dur">4:20</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">The Middle Eye</div><div class="track-desc">Seeing from the place between autobiography and imagination.</div></div><div class="track-dur">5:10</div></div>
</div>

<div class="audio-section">
  <div class="audio-section-title">Noir Song Frequencies</div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">Fourteen Frequencies</div><div class="track-desc">A sound installation mapping the frequencies between noise and listening.</div></div><div class="track-dur">12:40</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">Peat Bog Notes Cliff</div><div class="track-desc">Everything preserved in peat survives. Notes at the precipice.</div></div><div class="track-dur">8:15</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">Dumb Shaft Flue</div><div class="track-desc">Sound travels through shafts. What rises was never meant to be heard.</div></div><div class="track-dur">6:50</div></div>
  <div class="audio-track"><div class="track-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="8,5 19,12 8,19"/></svg></div><div class="track-info"><div class="track-title">Thunder Fireworks Lapdog Hide</div><div class="track-desc">Three kinds of noise that make a small animal seek shelter.</div></div><div class="track-dur">5:30</div></div>
</div>

</body>
</html>